TITLE: Episode 139 - Crushing Crispy Bois with Whipping Spoon
DESCRIPTION: It's the end of the month. It's time to find out what we missed while Whip has been planting almonds or harvesting them or whatever, talk about what we learned, have a good time, and talk about whatever is on our minds. This is the monthly venting and you are invited.
